727305f-a.text:
Main Avenue, south side, east of 30th Avenue, showing the New Astoria Live Poultry Market.
P. L. Sperr  June 2, 1927

727306f-b.text:
Main Avenue, at 30th Avenue. The tenements are on the north side of Main Avenue, and in the foreground is 30th Avenue. The gas station occupies a triangular apex.

Geo. D. Chinn  April, 1937
